data.description: Cute 3 bed, 2 bath home on .2 acres in a great neighborhood.  This home has carpet in the bedrooms and linoleum in the kitchen and baths.  The back yard is fenced which is great for the kids and dogs.  Solar panels have added to this home to save on the electric bill and when the power goes out you do not have to worry when everyone else is without power.  Great location, 1 mile to the Lost Plantation Golf Club and Rincon Elementary School and very close to all the shopping!!
